description:
James tells of his early life and how he became the leader of the church in Jerusalem. He explains the problems that led to the First Council at Jerusalem and the outcomes from that meeting, then shows how their decisions were instrumental to the future of Christianity. The basis for this episode is Acts 15.

Scripture
Acts 15: 1-29, 1 Corinthians 15:7

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Andy Axewell
